column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec, sp.modelMag_u,sp.modelMag_g,sp.modelMag_r,sp.modelMag_i,sp.modelMag_z,    (sp.modelMag_u-sp.modelMag_r) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_r-sp.modelMag_i) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_r-sp.modelMag_z) as &&&, (sp.modelMag_g-sp.modelMag_r) as &&&, p.petroRad_u,p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z,   p.petroRadErr_u,p.petroRadErr_g, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroRadErr_i, p.petroRadErr_z,    sp.class as obj_sp_type, sp.subclass as obj_sp_subtype, sp.z as redshift, em.bpt as em_sp_type, em.redshift as em_redshift, em.EW_Hb_# as Hb_EW, em.Flux_Hb_# as Hb_flux, em.Flux_OIII_# as OIII_#_flux, em.Flux_OIII_#_Err as OIII_#_flux,   sp.specobjid   into mydb.dr1#_Ports_rainbowpeas_sample    FROM    SpecPhoto as sp JOIN PhotoObj as p ON sp.objid=p.objid JOIN emissionLinesPort as em on sp.specobjid=em.specobjid  WHERE   em.EW_Hb_# > #
